rows.label: qst200717_msg0001
rows.name:
Ahh, that mushroom we all ate
was the literal best!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0002
rows.name:
You'd know, Idaten, you ate
for three as always!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0004
rows.name:
It musta been, since you ate
three people's worth!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0005
rows.name: I hope that was enough for you?

rows.label: qst200717_msg0006
rows.name:
You certainly ate with what can only
be termed a healthy appetite.

rows.label: qst200717_msg0008
rows.name:
Idaten, buddy, you sure like eating.
It was a marvel, watching you nosh!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0010
rows.name:
Mmm...
I'm sure I could eat more!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0011
rows.name:
After all, there's still plenty of things
in the world that I haven't tried yet!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0012
rows.name: I wanna find and eat them all!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0014
rows.name:
And also...
The Nopon seem to look up to me, so I
wanna stay the speed-eating champion!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0015
rows.name:
I'll rise to any challenge!
Tora's, Yumyum's, or whatever you
put before me, dear Driver.

rows.label: qst200717_msg0016
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Ohohoho...
Those speed eating contests sure are
a cheap way to fill a tummy!
